{
  "snp2.14:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 2.14 ",
  "snp2.14:0.2": "Dhammikasutta ",
  "snp2.14:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
  "snp2.14:1.2": "ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṁ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
  "snp2.14:1.3": "Atha kho dhammiko upāsako pañcahi upāsakasatehi saddhiṁ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṁ abhivādetvā ekamantaṁ nisīdi. Ekamantaṁ nisinno kho dhammiko upāsako bhagavantaṁ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "snp2.14:2.1": "“Pucchāmi taṁ gotama bhūripañña, ",
  "snp2.14:2.2": "Kathaṅkaro sāvako sādhu hoti; ",
  "snp2.14:2.3": "Yo vā agārā anagārameti, ",
  "snp2.14:2.4": "Agārino vā panupāsakāse. ",
  "snp2.14:3.1": "Tuvañhi lokassa sadevakassa, ",
  "snp2.14:3.2": "Gatiṁ pajānāsi parāyaṇañca; ",
  "snp2.14:3.3": "Na catthi tulyo nipuṇatthadassī, ",
  "snp2.14:3.4": "Tuvañhi buddhaṁ pavaraṁ vadanti. ",
  "snp2.14:4.1": "Sabbaṁ tuvaṁ ñāṇamavecca dhammaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:4.2": "Pakāsesi satte anukampamāno; ",
  "snp2.14:4.3": "Vivaṭṭacchadosi samantacakkhu, ",
  "snp2.14:4.4": "Virocasi vimalo sabbaloke. ",
  "snp2.14:5.1": "Āgañchi te santike nāgarājā, ",
  "snp2.14:5.2": "Erāvaṇo nāma jinoti sutvā; ",
  "snp2.14:5.3": "Sopi tayā mantayitvājjhagamā, ",
  "snp2.14:5.4": "Sādhūti sutvāna patītarūpo. ",
  "snp2.14:6.1": "Rājāpi taṁ vessavaṇo kuvero, ",
  "snp2.14:6.2": "Upeti dhammaṁ paripucchamāno; ",
  "snp2.14:6.3": "Tassāpi tvaṁ pucchito brūsi dhīra, ",
  "snp2.14:6.4": "So cāpi sutvāna patītarūpo. ",
  "snp2.14:7.1": "Ye kecime titthiyā vādasīlā, ",
  "snp2.14:7.2": "Ājīvakā vā yadi vā nigaṇṭhā; ",
  "snp2.14:7.3": "Paññāya taṁ nātitaranti sabbe, ",
  "snp2.14:7.4": "Ṭhito vajantaṁ viya sīghagāmiṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:8.1": "Ye kecime brāhmaṇā vādasīlā, ",
  "snp2.14:8.2": "Vuddhā cāpi brāhmaṇā santi keci; ",
  "snp2.14:8.3": "Sabbe tayi atthabaddhā bhavanti, ",
  "snp2.14:8.4": "Ye cāpi aññe vādino maññamānā. ",
  "snp2.14:9.1": "Ayañhi dhammo nipuṇo sukho ca, ",
  "snp2.14:9.2": "Yoyaṁ tayā bhagavā suppavutto; ",
  "snp2.14:9.3": "Tameva sabbepi sussūsamānā, ",
  "snp2.14:9.4": "Taṁ no vada pucchito buddhaseṭṭha. ",
  "snp2.14:10.1": "Sabbepime bhikkhavo sannisinnā, ",
  "snp2.14:10.2": "Upāsakā cāpi tatheva sotuṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:10.3": "Suṇantu dhammaṁ vimalenānubuddhaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:10.4": "Subhāsitaṁ vāsavasseva devā”. ",
  "snp2.14:11.1": "“Suṇātha me bhikkhavo sāvayāmi vo, ",
  "snp2.14:11.2": "Dhammaṁ dhutaṁ tañca carātha sabbe; ",
  "snp2.14:11.3": "Iriyāpathaṁ pabbajitānulomikaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:11.4": "Sevetha naṁ atthadaso mutīmā. ",
  "snp2.14:12.1": "No ve vikāle vicareyya bhikkhu, ",
  "snp2.14:12.2": "Gāme ca piṇḍāya careyya kāle; ",
  "snp2.14:12.3": "Akālacāriñhi sajanti saṅgā, ",
  "snp2.14:12.4": "Tasmā vikāle na caranti buddhā. ",
  "snp2.14:13.1": "Rūpā ca saddā ca rasā ca gandhā, ",
  "snp2.14:13.2": "Phassā ca ye sammadayanti satte; ",
  "snp2.14:13.3": "Etesu dhammesu vineyya chandaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:13.4": "Kālena so pavise pātarāsaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:14.1": "Piṇḍañca bhikkhu samayena laddhā, ",
  "snp2.14:14.2": "Eko paṭikkamma raho nisīde; ",
  "snp2.14:14.3": "Ajjhattacintī na mano bahiddhā, ",
  "snp2.14:14.4": "Nicchāraye saṅgahitattabhāvo. ",
  "snp2.14:15.1": "Sacepi so sallape sāvakena, ",
  "snp2.14:15.2": "Aññena vā kenaci bhikkhunā vā; ",
  "snp2.14:15.3": "Dhammaṁ paṇītaṁ tamudāhareyya, ",
  "snp2.14:15.4": "Na pesuṇaṁ nopi parūpavādaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:16.1": "Vādañhi eke paṭiseniyanti, ",
  "snp2.14:16.2": "Na te pasaṁsāma parittapaññe; ",
  "snp2.14:16.3": "Tato tato ne pasajanti saṅgā, ",
  "snp2.14:16.4": "Cittañhi te tattha gamenti dūre. ",
  "snp2.14:17.1": "Piṇḍaṁ vihāraṁ sayanāsanañca, ",
  "snp2.14:17.2": "Āpañca saṅghāṭirajūpavāhanaṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:17.3": "Sutvāna dhammaṁ sugatena desitaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:17.4": "Saṅkhāya seve varapaññasāvako. ",
  "snp2.14:18.1": "Tasmā hi piṇḍe sayanāsane ca, ",
  "snp2.14:18.2": "Āpe ca saṅghāṭirajūpavāhane; ",
  "snp2.14:18.3": "Etesu dhammesu anūpalitto, ",
  "snp2.14:18.4": "Bhikkhu yathā pokkhare vāribindu. ",
  "snp2.14:19.1": "Gahaṭṭhavattaṁ pana vo vadāmi, ",
  "snp2.14:19.2": "Yathākaro sāvako sādhu hoti; ",
  "snp2.14:19.3": "Na hesa labbhā sapariggahena, ",
  "snp2.14:19.4": "Phassetuṁ yo kevalo bhikkhudhammo. ",
  "snp2.14:20.1": "Pāṇaṁ na hane na ca ghātayeyya, ",
  "snp2.14:20.2": "Na cānujaññā hanataṁ paresaṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:20.3": "Sabbesu bhūtesu nidhāya daṇḍaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:20.4": "Ye thāvarā ye ca tasā santi loke. ",
  "snp2.14:21.1": "Tato adinnaṁ parivajjayeyya, ",
  "snp2.14:21.2": "Kiñci kvaci sāvako bujjhamāno; ",
  "snp2.14:21.3": "Na hāraye harataṁ nānujaññā, ",
  "snp2.14:21.4": "Sabbaṁ adinnaṁ parivajjayeyya. ",
  "snp2.14:22.1": "Abrahmacariyaṁ parivajjayeyya, ",
  "snp2.14:22.2": "Aṅgārakāsuṁ jalitaṁva viññū; ",
  "snp2.14:22.3": "Asambhuṇanto pana brahmacariyaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:22.4": "Parassa dāraṁ na atikkameyya. ",
  "snp2.14:23.1": "Sabhaggato vā parisaggato vā, ",
  "snp2.14:23.2": "Ekassa veko na musā bhaṇeyya; ",
  "snp2.14:23.3": "Na bhāṇaye bhaṇataṁ nānujaññā, ",
  "snp2.14:23.4": "Sabbaṁ abhūtaṁ parivajjayeyya. ",
  "snp2.14:24.1": "Majjañca pānaṁ na samācareyya, ",
  "snp2.14:24.2": "Dhammaṁ imaṁ rocaye yo gahaṭṭho; ",
  "snp2.14:24.3": "Na pāyaye pivataṁ nānujaññā, ",
  "snp2.14:24.4": "Ummādanantaṁ iti naṁ viditvā. ",
  "snp2.14:25.1": "Madā hi pāpāni karonti bālā, ",
  "snp2.14:25.2": "Kārenti caññepi jane pamatte; ",
  "snp2.14:25.3": "Etaṁ apuññāyatanaṁ vivajjaye, ",
  "snp2.14:25.4": "Ummādanaṁ mohanaṁ bālakantaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:26.1": "Pāṇaṁ na hane na cādinnamādiye, ",
  "snp2.14:26.2": "Musā na bhāse na ca majjapo siyā; ",
  "snp2.14:26.3": "Abrahmacariyā virameyya methunā, ",
  "snp2.14:26.4": "Rattiṁ na bhuñjeyya vikālabhojanaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:27.1": "Mālaṁ na dhāre na ca gandhamācare, ",
  "snp2.14:27.2": "Mañce chamāyaṁ va sayetha santhate; ",
  "snp2.14:27.3": "Etañhi aṭṭhaṅgikamāhuposathaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:27.4": "Buddhena dukkhantagunā pakāsitaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:28.1": "Tato ca pakkhassupavassuposathaṁ, ",
  "snp2.14:28.2": "Cātuddasiṁ pañcadasiñca aṭṭhamiṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:28.3": "Pāṭihāriyapakkhañca pasannamānaso, ",
  "snp2.14:28.4": "Aṭṭhaṅgupetaṁ susamattarūpaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:29.1": "Tato ca pāto upavutthuposatho, ",
  "snp2.14:29.2": "Annena pānena ca bhikkhusaṅghaṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:29.3": "Pasannacitto anumodamāno, ",
  "snp2.14:29.4": "Yathārahaṁ saṁvibhajetha viññū. ",
  "snp2.14:30.1": "Dhammena mātāpitaro bhareyya, ",
  "snp2.14:30.2": "Payojaye dhammikaṁ so vaṇijjaṁ; ",
  "snp2.14:30.3": "Etaṁ gihī vattayamappamatto, ",
  "snp2.14:30.4": "Sayampabhe nāma upeti deve”ti. ",
  "snp2.14:30.5": "Dhammikasuttaṁ cuddasamaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:30.6": "Cūḷavaggo dutiyo. ",
  "snp2.14:31.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
  "snp2.14:31.1": "Ratanāmagandho hiri ca, ",
  "snp2.14:31.2": "maṅgalaṁ sūcilomena; ",
  "snp2.14:31.3": "Dhammacariyañca brāhmaṇo, ",
  "snp2.14:31.4": "nāvā kiṁsīlamuṭṭhānaṁ. ",
  "snp2.14:32.1": "Rāhulo puna kappo ca, ",
  "snp2.14:32.2": "paribbājaniyaṁ tathā; ",
  "snp2.14:32.3": "Dhammikañca viduno āhu, ",
  "snp2.14:32.4": "cūḷavagganti cuddasāti. "
}